    "name": "Rivalia: Dungeon Raiders",
    "steam_appid": 1872500,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "你有没有想象过一觉醒来，发现自己和三个完全陌生的人被困在一个时空循环中？我相信你有。那么，磨好你的剑，补充你的箭筒，喝下法力药水，做好准备，因为如果你想打败邪恶的小丑和他的随从，控制了里瓦利亚城堡的可怕的怪物，你会需要它。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >4个主要人物，1个恶棍</h2>在这个滑稽的Roguelite冒险和单人ARPG游戏中，你将控制4个主要角色，寻求结束Rivalia的诅咒并使王国恢复正常。你将控制他们中的一个，能够在任何时候切换角色。但你不会孤军奋战，你的盟友将在史诗般的实时战斗中与你并肩作战!<br><br><br><strong>Ashelin</strong><br>你是那些喜欢打的人之一吗？Ashelin 不会让你失望。释放你内心的恶魔，在你的敌人中播下混乱的种子，用强大的刀法和恶魔的力量，让你吸收他们的灵魂。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/f9aec9eb361800c3ac376d92d3e91732.poster.avif?t=1677498388\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/f9aec9eb361800c3ac376d92d3e91732.webm?t=1677498388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/f9aec9eb361800c3ac376d92d3e91732.mp4?t=1677498388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Halmor</strong><br>寻找速度和灵巧？不要犹豫了，请找Halmor。结合敏捷的近战和安全的远程战斗的优点，用你强大的速度在后方击败敌人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/ab1a2151f45522125c5ba5d6304991b4.poster.avif?t=1677498388\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/ab1a2151f45522125c5ba5d6304991b4.webm?t=1677498388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/ab1a2151f45522125c5ba5d6304991b4.mp4?t=1677498388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Yhorm</strong><br>想看到自己被敌人包围并嘲笑他们甚甚至无法移动你？Yhorm是正确的选择。利用这个巨人的强悍，嘲弄你周围的敌人，保护你的盟友。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/e7c21cabe8534832293661e47779a358.poster.avif?t=1677498388\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/e7c21cabe8534832293661e47779a358.webm?t=1677498388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/e7c21cabe8534832293661e47779a358.mp4?t=1677498388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Evanya</strong><br>你宁愿装酷，让你的盟友做肮脏的工作吗？ 是你的选择。由于元素的力量，你的目标将是帮助你的盟友，为他们提供治疗、护盾，并对你的敌人造成改变的状态。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/5263f6df53c76bfb95b0f79f496018e1.poster.avif?t=1677498388\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/5263f6df53c76bfb95b0f79f496018e1.webm?t=1677498388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/5263f6df53c76bfb95b0f79f496018e1.mp4?t=1677498388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 。<br><br><strong>Ciceron</strong><br>那么，如果没有一个疯狂的反派来引爆它，一个伟大的故事会是什么？对 Evanya来说，他只不过是一个小丑。Ashelin来说，他是一个要追捕的恶魔。但对所有人来说，他已经成为使Rivalia恢复正常的主要目标。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/7f001cfdfee61a1780da8cc3b1638e44.poster.avif?t=1677498388\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/7f001cfdfee61a1780da8cc3b1638e44.webm?t=1677498388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/7f001cfdfee61a1780da8cc3b1638e44.mp4?t=1677498388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拯救王国的战斗</h2> 。<br><br><strong>程序性地牢的混乱</strong><br>Rivalia的城堡已经成为一个恶魔小丑的游乐场，这只能说明一件事....。准备好卷入一场完全的混乱，在其中你将穿过充满陷阱和挑战的巨大程序性地牢，在其中你可以探索巨大而气派的城堡、充满雄伟陵墓的阴暗墓地以及充满火焰和熔岩的黑暗洞穴...... 听起来很有趣，不是吗？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/dbc9270fb77066d8c72c2c3d2cd5d5b4.poster.avif?t=1677498388\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/dbc9270fb77066d8c72c2c3d2cd5d5b4.webm?t=1677498388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/dbc9270fb77066d8c72c2c3d2cd5d5b4.mp4?t=1677498388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 。<br><br><strong>击倒王国的敌人</strong><br>如果没有一堆敌人可以打，那么RPG游戏会是什么呢？钙做的战士，调皮的小恶魔，巨大的拳击龟.... 各种匪夷所思的敌人都会为小丑服务，保卫他们的领地，甚至在马厩里也发现了恐龙的身影! 史诗般的战斗是有保证的!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/6f73b35b709ddff237a9132739989336.poster.avif?t=1677498388\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/6f73b35b709ddff237a9132739989336.webm?t=1677498388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1872500/extras/6f73b35b709ddff237a9132739989336.mp4?t=1677498388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 。<br><br><strong>击败守护者</strong><br>Ciceron下的随从并不只是由弱小的奴仆组成。他的守护者是具有独特战斗机制的强大生物，他们将保护每一个地牢，并提供一个伟大的最后挑战。你能胜任这项任务吗？<br><br><strong>掠夺、锻造和强化自己</strong><br>击败敌人，用他们自己的材料制造装备。你还可以将这些装备组合起来，获得各种力量，并使用它们来对付你的敌人。多么残酷... 你确定小丑是这个故事中的坏人吗？",
